  "title": "Improving the Google Chat and Gmail search experience on web and mobile",
  "content": "<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">What’s changing</h3><div>In order to help you find more accurate and customized search suggestions and results, we’re introducing three features that improve the Google Chat and Gmail search experience on web and mobile:</div><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li><b>Search suggestions:</b> Search-query suggestions based on your past search history in Chat will now appear as you type in the Chat search bar. This will help you quickly recall important messages, files, and more on mobile.&nbsp;</li></ul><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; display: inline; text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg-7EksxR7AtcTYUbhOGOsyJwFpgThN9Id9EOiOzNh5luxUTFsSb5k3TqScwHBrscnoyF2x9xS13OMYtVgRVi1ZgOVQ5HFYLS0wVhD-AP1tG1Hmjob0m6Ge_IqO8y5A-JOtySyfzPWB9abRbP68AjelP7lWn6Ws-FsDmdHCEDKK2wm_wL4Ev2u1U79E/s1234/Search%20suggestions.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1234\" data-original-width=\"600\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg-7EksxR7AtcTYUbhOGOsyJwFpgThN9Id9EOiOzNh5luxUTFsSb5k3TqScwHBrscnoyF2x9xS13OMYtVgRVi1ZgOVQ5HFYLS0wVhD-AP1tG1Hmjob0m6Ge_IqO8y5A-JOtySyfzPWB9abRbP68AjelP7lWn6Ws-FsDmdHCEDKK2wm_wL4Ev2u1U79E/w312-h640/Search%20suggestions.png\" width=\"312\" /></a></div></div></div><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li><b>Gmail labels:</b> You can now search messages under a specific <a href=\"https://support.google.com/mail/answer/118708?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop\">Gmail label</a> in the app to return results only within that label. You can also use search chips in the Gmail search bar to refine label searches.&nbsp;</li></ul><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhccjujqq0yy-O10JnJ-mjSyCx2uwS3jLVCyjcbsl1WgQS8CP5laxeobiJPjpkw39ECW6b0vYjBIAAtvKJhP9lHvSF5a3tdkJmcZg085SybtpWqmEiDJemgJyb-Wy9Qc411cazwgi4x4kdzpM8h3CZ1dqlyi04tptKBqdEKpwR-UMlH8X8bJJvMQxaO/s800/left-drawer-labelsearch.gif\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"800\" data-original-width=\"368\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhccjujqq0yy-O10JnJ-mjSyCx2uwS3jLVCyjcbsl1WgQS8CP5laxeobiJPjpkw39ECW6b0vYjBIAAtvKJhP9lHvSF5a3tdkJmcZg085SybtpWqmEiDJemgJyb-Wy9Qc411cazwgi4x4kdzpM8h3CZ1dqlyi04tptKBqdEKpwR-UMlH8X8bJJvMQxaO/w294-h640/left-drawer-labelsearch.gif\" width=\"294\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg2xjV-pBYOYqC3zWkgzF3JMxeFkNQjZxUai3gZwd8xTJa5wQqP1RLqpEhUJ2q26NXs8UsrWr9ufZiLM4zPeGIhFIP33iJgq4m1Hjq2WqsWAXlKPoFdy00l7PLg3FsEvo4TVjqTT8gVT1ySeKfKsfoGm2LrGpBZxSEmbo5IkluSXcD9f4hmfAFZzQVl/s800/search-bar-journey.gif\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"800\" data-original-width=\"368\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg2xjV-pBYOYqC3zWkgzF3JMxeFkNQjZxUai3gZwd8xTJa5wQqP1RLqpEhUJ2q26NXs8UsrWr9ufZiLM4zPeGIhFIP33iJgq4m1Hjq2WqsWAXlKPoFdy00l7PLg3FsEvo4TVjqTT8gVT1ySeKfKsfoGm2LrGpBZxSEmbo5IkluSXcD9f4hmfAFZzQVl/w294-h640/search-bar-journey.gif\" width=\"294\" /></a><br /></div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li><b>Related results:</b> For Gmail search-queries that return no results, related results will be shown to improve the overall search experience.&nbsp;</li></ul></div><div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhPlrh3YJNGyl0kAXq7aNsGlBYQPy98UWxMMtwfMlPXwDS_hvhTeG_nqH4mEs_k671lMyxWcZjSGouhZ19yx4AsVmUnQ3Ax8OvgVP0SpNxMGlgLl3EBOMd5VULoMyUhxnJR7cijQerPM0D_nl8iscBW78bilOJ-B2alxM6cpGKKudAl7Bp0GOe76FJT/s2076/related%20results.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1294\" data-original-width=\"2076\" height=\"398\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhPlrh3YJNGyl0kAXq7aNsGlBYQPy98UWxMMtwfMlPXwDS_hvhTeG_nqH4mEs_k671lMyxWcZjSGouhZ19yx4AsVmUnQ3Ax8OvgVP0SpNxMGlgLl3EBOMd5VULoMyUhxnJR7cijQerPM0D_nl8iscBW78bilOJ-B2alxM6cpGKKudAl7Bp0GOe76FJT/w640-h398/related%20results.png\" width=\"640\" /></a></div></div><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Getting started&nbsp;</h3><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li><b>Admins:</b> There is no admin control for this feature.&nbsp;</li><li><b>End users:</b> Visit the Help Center to learn more about <a href=\"https://support.google.com/mail/answer/6593?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop\">Search in Gmail</a> and <a href=\"https://support.google.com/chat/answer/7655805?hl=en\">Search for Google Chat messages</a>.&nbsp;</li></ul><br /></div><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Rollout pace&nbsp;</h3><div><b>Search suggestions:&nbsp;</b></div><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li>This feature is now available on Android devices</li><li>Rollout to iOS devices will complete by the end of October&nbsp;</li></ul></div><div><b>Gmail labels:&nbsp;</b></div><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li>This feature is now available on Android and iOS devices&nbsp;</li></ul></div><div><b>Related results:&nbsp;</b></div><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li>This feature is now available on web&nbsp;</li></ul></div><div><br /></div><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Availability&nbsp;</h3><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li>Available to all Google Workspace customers, as well as legacy G Suite Basic and Business customers&nbsp;</li><li>Available to users with personal Google Accounts&nbsp;</li></ul></div><div><br /></div><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Resources&nbsp;</h3><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/mail/answer/6593?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop\">Google Help: Search in Gmail&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/chat/answer/7655805?hl=en\">Google Help: Search for Google Chat messages&nbsp;</a></li></ul></div><div><br /></div><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Roadmap&nbsp;</h3><div><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li>Two of these features were listed as an <a href=\"https://support.google.com/a/table/7539891\">upcoming release</a>.</li></ul></div><br />",
